<headline>Special Weather Statement issued December 31 at 10:41AM EST  by NWS New York City - Upton</headline>
<description>Areas of fog, locally dense at times, will continue through early
this afternoon. Visibilities may be reduced to one quarter to one
half mile in the fog.
Motorists should be prepared for rapidly changing visibilities and
drive with extra caution when encountering this fog. Use low beam
headlights and allow for extra spacing between vehicles.</description>
